column5: Not sweet at all, almost salty
both were tart and not super sweet, but better flavor than the 2-26 harvest. Most of the water has just been H20 rather than solution.
Both plants had split tomatoes that were mostly against the sides of the box.
accidentially removed one non-ripe... and one way over ripe (So did not weigh those)
One non-ripe fell off the blue night plant while harvesting (not included in weights)
Massive pruning done to control and blue light. Some pruning done to the +basil plant
